Carragher: &quot;I think the brilliant thing for Liverpool is that it's Klopp's second full season in English football. January was a bit of a nightmare for Liverpool last season because of injuries, a loss of form and Sadio Man&eacute; going away.&quot;<br />
<br />
Carragher: &quot;He's getting it right now - changing players at the right time. He's got a bench now which looks like a bench a top club should have - he didn't have that last season. Hopefully you'll see Liverpool get through this period.&quot;

Klopp on Spartak: &quot;It's THE game. We are only part of the CL because we want to go to the next round. If we win we are through - that's cool.&quot;<br />
<br />
Klopp: &quot;We are stronger than we were when we played them but they are stronger too. They have some important offensive players back.&quot;

Klopp on Everton: &quot;We have enough time after tomorrow night to think about Sunday's game. We won't hesitate to line up our best team. Even when we've changed a lot it was always about bringing in these players for concentration, skills and for fresh legs.&quot;<br />
<br />
Klopp on CBs: &quot;Much better. Klavan and Gomez are back. Matip and Lallana still out.&quot;

Klopp: &quot;We are in a part of the season where you should see that we've worked together so far. We had little drops and games which were not as good as we should have expected. Tottenham is the most obvious one.&quot;<br />
<br />
Klopp: &quot;We learned from it. But I cannot take it for granted and neither can the boys. We need to prove our quality every day. Tomorrow is a very important match for us. I don't want to make it bigger than it is, but it is very big.&quot;

Sadio Mane on being rested recently: &quot;Each player would love to play every game but we're Liverpool with a lot of big players.&quot;<br />
<br />
Mane: &quot;It's too early to speak about the derby, we need to concentrate on Spartak. This is one of the biggest games of the season for us.&quot;

Mane on Salah: &quot;I am happy for Mo. He's a very important player for us.&quot;<br />
<br />
Mane on Coutinho's FKs: &quot;I am trying to learn from him!&quot;
